Happy #indigenouspeoplesday . Some lightness to share in these sad times. Meet Sage Romero @digitalndn who is sharing his talents and keeping indigenous culture alive through dance, art and education. He is the founder of the Akamya Culture Group in Big Pine, CA, whom I hope you will support. (https://www.akamya.com/). I had the good fortune making these photos with him this past summer in Washoe ancestral land, aka Lake Tahoe. Watching Sage do the hoop dance, which is so spiritual and infused with the shapes of nature, is downright transformative. 
#akamya #nativeamericandance #nativeamericandancers #hoopdance #hoopdancer #sageromero #digitalndn #indigenousart #indigenousdance
